gars is a Rust background service inspired by GenericAgent:
https://github.com/lsdefine/GenericAgent

The original GenericAgent project is licensed under the MIT License:
Copyright (c) 2025 lsdefine

This repository preserves the core design ideas, not the Python implementation:
- a small reusable tool surface instead of many narrow tools
- layered memory with minimal pointers and action-verified updates
- token-frugal context management through compression, truncation, and anchors
- self-improving SOPs and reflect/scheduler style autonomy

No Python source files from the original project are copied into this repository.
